_(Perugino)\" title=\"Lamentation over the Dead Christ (Perugino)\">Lamentation over the Dead Christ</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Decemviri_Altarpiece\" title=\"Decemviri Altarpiece\">Decemviri Altarpiece</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/San_Pietro_Polyptych\" title=\"San Pietro Polyptych\">San Pietro Polyptych</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Fano_Altarpiece\" title=\"Fano Altarpiece\">Fano Altarpiece</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/San_Francesco_al_Prato_Resurrection\" title=\"San Francesco al Prato Resurrection\">San Francesco al Prato Resurrection</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Tezi_Altarpiece\" title=\"Tezi Altarpiece\">Tezi Altarpiece</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Vallombrosa_Altarpiece\" title=\"Vallombrosa Altarpiece\">Vallombrosa Altarpiece</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Madonna_in_Glory_with_Saints\" title=\"Madonna in Glory with Saints\">Madonna in Glory with Saints</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Marriage_of_the_Virgin_(Perugino)\" title=\"Marriage of the Virgin (Perugino)\">Marriage of the Virgin</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Battle_Between_Love_and_Chastity\" title=\"The Battle Between Love and Chastity\">The Battle Between Love and Chastity</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Annunziata_Polyptych\" title=\"Annunziata Polyptych\">Annunziata Polyptych</a></i></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Sansepolcro_Altarpiece\" title=\"Sansepolcro Altarpiece\">Sansepolcro Altarpiece</a></i></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<div role=\"navigation\" class=\"navbox\" aria-labelledby=\"Decoration_of_the_Sistine_Chapel\" style=\"padding:3px\"><table class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;color:inherit\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"3\" style=\"background: gold\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist navbar mini\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template:Sistine_Chapel\" title=\"Template:Sistine Chapel\"><abbr title=\"View this template\" style=\"background: gold;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">v</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-talk\"><a href=\"/wiki/Template_talk:Sistine_Chapel\" title=\"Template talk:Sistine Chapel\"><abbr title=\"Discuss this template\" style=\"background: gold;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">t</abbr></a></li><li class=\"nv-edit\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Template:Sistine_Chapel&amp;action=edit\"><abbr title=\"Edit this template\" style=\"background: gold;;background:none transparent;border:none;-moz-box-shadow:none;-webkit-box-shadow:none;box-shadow:none; padding:0;\">e</abbr></a></li></ul></div><div id=\"Decoration_of_the_Sistine_Chapel\" style=\"font-size:114%;margin:0 4em\">Decoration of the <a href=\"/wiki/Sistine_Chapel\" title=\"Sistine Chapel\">Sistine Chapel</a></div></th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\"background: gold;width:1%\">Life of <a href=\"/wiki/Moses\" title=\"Moses\">Moses</a></th><td class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\" style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Moses_Leaving_to_Egypt_(Perugino)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Moses Leaving to Egypt (Perugino)\">Moses Leaving to Egypt</a></i> <sup>1</sup></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Youth_of_Moses\" title=\"Youth of Moses\">Youth of Moses</a></i> <sup>2</sup></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Crossing_of_the_Red_Sea_(Sistine_Chapel)\" title=\"The Crossing of the Red Sea (Sistine Chapel)\">The Crossing of the Red Sea</a></i> <sup>3/4/5</sup></li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/wiki/Descent_from_Mount_Sinai_(Sistine_Chapel)\" title=\"Descent from Mount Sinai (Sistine Chapel)\">The Descent from Mount Sinai</a></i> <sup>3/6</sup></li>\n<